        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "You can associate a display link with multiple input modes. While the run loop is executing in a mode you have specified, the display link notifies the target when new frames are required."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "The run loop retains the display link. To remove the display link from all run loops, send an "
